{"title":"- Uso de Anticoagulantes Orales Directos (DOACs)-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/- Uso de Anticoagulantes Orales Directos (DOACs)-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"\\\\*Uso de Anticoagulantes Orales Directos (DOACs): Guía Clínica 2024\\\\*\\N\\\\*(Basado en JACC 2024)\\\\*","guid":"YYBjrEDf8QUUkX-BSjJw6w","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Introducción","guid":"428ep8MXTrGbbJWDCGGkOA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Los anticoagulantes orales directos (DOACs) han emergido como una alternativa a\\Nlos antagonistas de la vitamina K (AVK) en varios escenarios clínicos.","guid":"qv_K8zrDIfmmIZVJowyXxg","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Indicaciones Establecidas para DOACs","guid":"kh9aXcWHqtculSnsXK9ZkQ","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"Fibrilación auricular no valvular","guid":"wuKRgTtBEX9e39JGJPcNFA","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"Tromboembolismo venoso (TEV)","guid":"TlMID_NH5yMjOJLBaF1HbA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"Prevención secundaria en pacientes con enfermedad cardiovascular estable","guid":"GIQrl5zKXkKQYqWcyPPWZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"Contraindicaciones para el Uso de DOACs","guid":"Mdx-kllckyEefSaCXKI8YA","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Válvulas cardíacas mecánicas","guid":"lO-vJLRSH4ExIkgNP-jy2A","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Fibrilación auricular reumática","guid":"OqGeSYO7WUlf_ymWVRDIJg","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"Síndrome antifosfolípido trombótico (APS)","guid":"NDQbTv8_UpWXMeZZIDMu-g","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"Reemplazo valvular aórtico transcatéter (TAVR)","guid":"Ul4-TNLIoRuoKBM8k0Gdig","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"Ictus embólico de origen indeterminado (ESUS)","guid":"PjPZJHnf1WOV-0A4nzTolg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"7","text":"Dispositivo de asistencia ventricular izquierda (LVAD)","guid":"y7srfIOp-C0QK8kFtH-2jQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"7","text":"Insuficiencia cardíaca con fracción de eyección reducida sin fibrilación auricular","guid":"6htnDcw_bnI3PtMDxlj5xA","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"1","text":"Escenarios de Incertidumbre","guid":"zllETSMDpWvyw33XMDA3Og","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Trombo ventricular izquierdo","guid":"_hkLVBk5tECtUpo_3hZyWg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Trombosis venosa asociada a catéter","guid":"C_8ydiruMrdCYBcwCysfLw","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"Trombosis venosa esplénica","guid":"P1QZXt0xrmKRrDnjZBjLBw","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"15","text":"Trombosis del seno venoso cerebral (CVST)","guid":"SDgNWXxlQX30y254ZmYlYA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"15","text":"Insuficiencia renal terminal (ESRD)","guid":"NF5zEqiWXqW5ctQYRFzT9Q","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"15","text":"Embarazo y lactancia","guid":"FFAcAdxWgtzyTbsq6QIDwA","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"15","text":"Enfermedad cardíaca congénita en adultos","guid":"Y8q7NlCDOQUq9f1PPxC7lA","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"15","text":"Hipertensión pulmonar tromboembólica crónica","guid":"CfUmyQXnaONboigUCztO6w","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"15","text":"Pacientes con índice de masa corporal (IMC) >45 kg/m² y postbariátricos","guid":"wOhYnuSwn8XOyWrbihHEUw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"15","text":"Trombocitopenia inducida por heparina (HIT)","guid":"pStwNzvNUtBl7eLPmBBsyQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Recomendaciones Específicas\\Nen Fibrilación Auricular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Se recomienda el uso de DOACs en FA, incluyendo\\Npacientes con síndrome coronario agudo.","guid":"sMu9caQh4QWo2ok6ndfoTg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"En intervención coronaria percutánea, combinar con inhibidor P2Y12\\N(preferentemente clopidogrel).","guid":"ibaqolpYa9c9YdhL1lv81g","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"En enfermedad coronaria crónica de bajo riesgo aterotrombótico,\\Nconsiderar suspender aspirina después de un año.","guid":"HZIobMWPRcyiAGVEpCSSPg","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"Indicados en FA con valvulopatías, excepto\\Nen casos de enfermedad reumática.","guid":"iKSGtE187FaEyolopUhXUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Evidencia Científica en\\NCondiciones Específicas","guid":"f_b7vlxZPr6-yzG68RqaCQ","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Válvulas Cardíacas\\NMecánicas","guid":"oK42SmU2d6BCY-zMX-Uxgg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Estudio\\NRE-ALIGN:","guid":"em6PzFFk45gD3eHHhbSgXA","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Comparación: Dabigatrán vs. Warfarina","guid":"AKYD98PTKzHqrxpqXnnayw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Población: 252 pacientes con válvulas mecánicas aórticas o mitrales","guid":"pejIhGD24QMVeFfMkID8oQ","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"Resultado: Estudio interrumpido por exceso de eventos\\Ntrombóticos y hemorrágicos en grupo dabigatrán","guid":"rJugDFHgJ42LpQNHgL8UzA","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"32","text":"Estudio\\NPROACT Xa:","guid":"evPCoadIfHN11kLag_BBxA","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Comparación: Apixabán vs. Warfarina","guid":"2xAf_dLQNH6CPk8ZVnjx1w","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Población: Pacientes con válvulas mecánicas On-X","guid":"U4dqE-nhFzf7iRwrIZ2ctg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Resultado: Interrumpido por altas tasas de trombosis en grupo apixabán","guid":"6ZTenCw9qu3AquBVArUvvg","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"32","text":"Conclusión: Se recomienda el uso de antagonistas de vitamina K (AVK) como tratamiento estándar.","guid":"JQk9lET1LKyTG0xtQcr_Wg","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"31","text":"Fibrilación Auricular\\NReumática","guid":"As0GvcqvASOKhKa_IIuT5A","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Estudio Clínico\\NPrincipal:","guid":"xleCSB9-ZasT65uUVw8j2g","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Población: 4, 531 pacientes","guid":"NSd_tHEtknFttxXQmhzIZg","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Definición: FA más enfermedad cardíaca reumática confirmada por ecocardiografía","guid":"4mwLDZKzz9H19WKKAJfKDQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"Intervención: Rivaroxabán 20 mg diarios","guid":"5ozIPHn6fQnFradJecbkCg","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"Resultados:","guid":"rvx8LHg9nruH0mgR0H34pw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"Aumento significativo en tasa de ictus","guid":"jajQgbPccg7EYfcn_IKYLQ","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"Incremento en embolismo sistémico","guid":"gzlq7npj3aKupP1x8XyY_Q","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"Mayor incidencia de infarto de miocardio y muerte","guid":"Ar3gE1RwaIAXdFgdLd8RJg","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"HR: 1.25 (IC 95%: 1.0-1.41)","guid":"b1-7k4noGtHVGqD2g38HOg","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"Sin diferencias significativas en sangrado mayor","guid":"s-THMGPTshv9o4QaCypMfA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"42","text":"Recomendación: Uso preferente de AVK para prevención de ictus.","guid":"0eCcqPSpHgUBlVxjCYroSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"31","text":"Síndrome Antifosfolípido\\NTrombótico","guid":"PvW90Ud1DHxthbf-0eBuIA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Evidencia Científica:","guid":"grZGd56C0LQmT3lkR-eFBg","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Ensayos Clínicos: 4 RCTs evaluaron seguridad y eficacia","guid":"w7j2kxKJYOLyABw820SPcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"Metaanálisis\\NPrincipal:","guid":"paIdcE5FFLUx3i1VRrQgEQ","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Población: 472 pacientes","guid":"Dri0nBOv6jyfTEa0ZeUPiA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Comparación: DOACs vs. warfarina","guid":"CRA0wkkYw5d57sFzrdMbmg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"Resultados:","guid":"n0K-AH9iuYtikFTIRYKRrQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Eventos trombóticos arteriales significativamente mayores con DOACs\\N(24 vs. 5 eventos; OR: 5.43)","guid":"mmBJ-p7fvrF7_EbXfAAWUg","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"Mayor riesgo de ictus (20 vs. 0; OR: 10.74)","guid":"QPp1Vs-wk_qHjNPTnL8HBQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"No hubo diferencias en recurrencia de TEV ni en sangrado mayor","guid":"gu9WBYON4SN_lN0yZE264g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"54","text":"Recomendación: Tratamiento de elección: Antagonistas de vitamina K (AVK) a largo plazo.","guid":"g_38W1LNqR1Y-41X3wi8BQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"31","text":"Reemplazo Valvular Aórtico\\NTranscatéter (TAVR)","guid":"xALwjwT2PJsnzd2VUDs5HQ","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Estudios\\NRealizados:","guid":"FCgPIkQ2zcFlSGODC6xCbA","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Primer\\NEstudio:","guid":"ce80IFCJhLv3vl0G0a1NoQ","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Intervención: Rivaroxabán + aspirina","guid":"4u2vQIA_HL7mdLjR8xcr7Q","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Comparador: Aspirina + clopidogrel","guid":"goLgQp8-X9xln0kOKSPKnA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Resultados: Mayor riesgo de muerte, aumento de eventos tromboembólicos y\\Nmayor riesgo de sangrado. Suspensión temprana del estudio.","guid":"cP1g1tj0_eoZ1azBlPyDIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"66","text":"Segundo\\NEstudio:","guid":"M0xGE8hDVr5RrnfUJFbbDQ","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"Comparación: Apixabán vs. tratamiento estándar","guid":"vGh_3xgnyPbWh2tSKjy1Jg","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"Resultados: Sin diferencias significativas","guid":"2JGtUQNGi7WkM-PL08ZRbw","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"66","text":"Estudios con\\NEdoxabán:","guid":"OSbVxHbyHLQow_M6EUbcAQ","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"Eficacia no inferior a warfarina","guid":"NteJzBMnDA